          <hr align="center" width="50%" height="5" />
          <p align="center">
            The Ford Everest is a mid-size SUV produced by Ford Motor Company
            since 2003.<br />
            Developed and destined mainly for the Asia-Pacific region with
            production centered in <br />Thailand, the first-generation Everest
            is based on the Mazda-based Ford Ranger pickup <br />truck, while
            the following generations is based on the globally-marketed T6
            Ranger.
          </p>
